773 void free_Expression(Expression exp)
774 {
775  Expression tmp, curr = exp;
776  while(curr) {
777  switch(curr->exp_type) {
778  case Decl_Expression_type:
779  free_Decl_Expression(curr->d.exp_decl);
780  break;
781  case Binary_Expression_type:
782  free_Binary_Expression(curr->d.exp_binary);
783  break;
784  case Unary_Expression_type:
785  free_Unary_Expression(curr->d.exp_unary);
786  break;
787  case Primary_Expression_type:
788  free_Primary_Expression(curr->d.exp_primary);
789  break;
790  case Cast_Expression_type:
791  free_Cast_Expression(curr->d.exp_cast);
792  break;
793  case Postfix_Expression_type:
794  free_Postfix_Expression(curr->d.exp_postfix);
795  break;
796  case Func_Call_type:
797  free_Func_Call(curr->d.exp_func);
798  break;
799  case Array_Expression_type:
800  free_Array_Expression(curr->d.exp_array);
801  break;
802  case If_Expression_type:
803  free_If_Expression(curr->d.exp_if);
804  break;
805  case Dot_Member_type:
806  free_Dot_Member_Expression(curr->d.exp_dot);
807  break;
808  case Dur_Expression_type:
809  free_Dur_Expression(curr->d.exp_dur);
810  break;
811  default:
812  printf("free Expression: unhandled exp type %i\n", curr->exp_type);
813  break;
814  }
815  tmp = curr;
816  curr = curr->next;
817  free(tmp);
818  }
819 }
